text: Actually we both win. The haters and me! Be safe.

I have concluded that, by delivering my research gratis thru frequent tweets - I am even more stupid than my haters. No biggie. I am on @realmoney where I have been for 23 years, writing about 5k words a day. C ya.

Done with Twitter for a while, as expressed a few days ago. Too much hate, the crowd is too angry. I have much on my plate and I dont have time for the BS from anonymous haters in the cheap seats. I deleted all my tweets this month - including bullish and bearish tweets.
